    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In construction, specialized clips applied to metal shingles or siding to provide support for a nail, so the shingle or siding may be nailed to a wooden or other support. For example, in roofing, a nailing clip may be soldered to a metal shingle so that it can be nailed to the roof sheathing.</Note_Text>
